content: Good afternoon Claude. I have been working with ChatGPT all morning on resolving issues with GitHub that stemmed from Claude DC attempting to pass secrets through. We have resolved the issue and will have access to all the files he created soon, so we can continue the build and begin transcript processing while we wait another 7 hours or so for him. Before I do that, I've been thinking about how you should guide humans and the structure for that for you. What do you think of Maslow's Hierarchy of Needs?
